{"tid":1392460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣嘅義士，你地好嗎?","createTime":"2019-07-31T17:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T02:18:21.000Z","uid":265197,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"21d0213a9a98ccace19d0173a2d4a776b58b078e","tid":1392460,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:59:27.000Z","msg":"我無忘記你地<br />\n好抱歉當日無同你地一齊入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地有無遇到咩困難係我地呢邊可以幫到手嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0789d60ad959a29117c315032c9dfaf67296d717","tid":1392460,"uid":265197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3bbf9f2362c4e5c919b98e441edf681f5e64ea","tid":1392460,"uid":265197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82272a7da70ed19c170d9e7e609ee2155a6eceb3","tid":1392460,"uid":6528,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:00:58.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年內落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年內！"},{"pid":"d8ab73a8fc5e539941e2ba7ddfb3ef1a8f650bec","tid":1392460,"uid":1444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:01:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"93628c193dee68ff90126e4cb075a6b9bc754aad","tid":1392460,"uid":171860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:03:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵朋友代post講下近況我地都好開心嫁啦"},{"pid":"0272c75595ad9b750884e8605cc2e4e09286ca30","tid":1392460,"uid":265197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:10:49.000Z","msg":"我地唔係忘記左你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係真係愈黎愈多事發生個個都好頭痕好攰<br />\n連文宣同推po都少左人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好擔心呀<br />\n每次都係周身痛住咁走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508a82bbf3abdccd7ea01deb8e162ce800ec3192","tid":1392460,"uid":54223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:38:47.000Z","msg":"visa 過左期？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0761df959c498532b24ae448c3f4db1aa5d3e395","tid":1392460,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:21:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc09c13c6639cad989bd35326e6d62a30c0afb1","tid":1392460,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T20:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce4688da86ace4f00141f55c31bd17aa0a9bf5e","tid":1392460,"uid":31539,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T20:16:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a138039125dff9dc5ff3b219fd1236564736219","tid":1392460,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T20:17:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6898015e9842acd15cea6a10d93f6f87c9b5a5af","tid":1392460,"uid":100930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T20:44:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ad27e1e6d197b4ee5be9238f8d586fc48223976","tid":1392460,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:12:55.000Z","msg":"8月5罷工見"},{"pid":"accd7a96882c0126cea9feb815185b74d2e9d124","tid":1392460,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:24:44.000Z","msg":"你地好嗎？"},{"pid":"0d7c921380ee5e32c28eb5d0059067f238496132","tid":1392460,"uid":270956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:35:46.000Z","msg":"你地好嗎？"},{"pid":"61e1792bf2324fd1aca90116e3195686ce1cc3ca","tid":1392460,"uid":49178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:40:41.000Z","msg":"有咩困難 記得要講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e7fa55f789b943c90fad29ec1ab834b356a8c8","tid":1392460,"uid":286825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:18:21.000Z","msg":"打個廣告：<br />\n台北市大安區永固商圈<br />\n台灣小型寶石工作室<br />\nRyan 寶石工作室<br />\n歡迎各位對寶石知識有興趣的香港人，<br />\n到店詳談寶石知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n零鳩零鳩鳩陸一柒一發"}]}